3a4697c84311d5fd","tid":294302,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"我想含小強好耐架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我！ 真係！ 好！肚！餓！呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead6a875e4fe1b53e1d502adba16ed4b82767027","tid":294302,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tonEFBu1K1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtonEFBu1K1c&d=2fYxIhFQhlO8Y94OsLuIXUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5762d5a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tonEFBu1K1c</a><br />\n停一停 , 諗一諗"},{"pid":"2090b3b9e701bcee55f6093321247dfa36f05561","tid":294302,"uid":43068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"食一隻，等12個鐘<br />\n<br />\n收錢"},{"pid":"1553d64455cf676f25d6a60e93b31ff49fead5ae","tid":294302,"uid":43068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內容如下:<br />\n參加者要將x隻小強(品種為棕色蟑螂)放入口中,以小強停留在口中的時間來賺取獎金。<span style=\"color: red;\">參加者不得試圖用任何方法殺死或吞食小強,</span>否則取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n1. 參加者需自行決定放份口中的小強數量, 以單隻計算, 每隻為10000 HKD。 例:小明將2隻小強放入口中3秒再取出, 將獲得10,000 x 2(小強數量) x 3 (秒數) = 60,000HKD<br />\n<br />\n2. 基於安全理由,本實驗計時上限為12小時。<br />\n<br />\n3. 本實驗並無限制參加者放入口中的小強數量, 但參加者<span style=\"color: red;\">有責任令小強存活,否則將從總獎金中扣減每隻10%</span>。 例:小明將3隻小強放入口中, 10秒後放棄, 將小強取出, 但發現當中有2隻小強死亡, 所得獎金將會變成: 10,000 x 3 x 10 x (1 - 10% x 2)= 240,000。<br />\n<br />\n來吧, 即管將小強放入口啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於小強太樣衰 我決定唔出圖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食左隻小強，表面扮含12個鐘，最後被衝入肚，<br />\n由主動扮被動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1d679be32a9d5d74d43b32c89e914c8b878f78","tid":294302,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"人地日本已經做緊啦 有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa550d3c56cb69a3beb0d0fd95fa2a95fc9beb2","tid":294302,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"除非你咬爛佢<br />\n如果唔係你要隻小強唔死難過死<br />\n話時話小強冇左個頭都可以存活1個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n1個鍾3600秒, 成3千幾萬<br />\n<br />\n含撚都得啦莫講話含甲由"},{"pid":"1ac3b8a053f9942436a00b8c3d140de83849d399","tid":294302,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:27:22.000Z","msg":"10000*10*100 = 1千萬<br />\n我夠了"},{"pid":"bec5f1c2dfa6d5adb43e7b313469928cf174126d","tid":294302,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"我100蚊都竹戈"},{"pid":"7639bd808c9bfe50c2a50f2d77ebc85b06ab9320","tid":294302,"uid":35420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我100蚊都竹戈</blockquote><br />\n我比夠200 你<br />\n你拍片表演我睇"},{"pid":"1e782fb0f63adf8b2d67d8d6face7c1e81e3c951","tid":294302,"uid":98,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0770d32002ca0a68cef118dc4cb3862959dd6f8","tid":294302,"uid"